0.title: Rules
0.body:
Rulebook viewable @ http://tinyurl.com/h5s8b3t

Setup: 
Everything has been randomized at the start.

- Library Spells
     Just take one spell from each level of each element from the library and put them face down on the spots above the board.  The level 3 spell should be on the bottom and the level 1 should be on the top.

- Spell Book
     Remove cards from the Right Side of the Spell Book until there are only 5 cards. Then take the top card from the Spell Book Cover deck and place it on top.  Remove all unused cards.

- Characters
    Pick your characters carefully to ensure the best chance at victory.  Then take then number of element cards listed on your character card into your hand.  All remaining Element x1 cards should be removed from the game.

Destroyed Cards:  All cards destroyed while playing the game should be set to the side of the board.  There is a game play element that can put them back into the game.
